## Project Overview

This is a **React + Vite** frontend application for an Inventory Management System. It communicates with a **Spring Boot backend API** running on `http://localhost:8088/api`.

**Key Technologies:**
- React 19.2 (Functional Components & Hooks)
- Vite 7.3 (Build tool & Dev server)
- Material-UI (MUI 5) - UI Component Library
- React Router 6 - Client-side routing
- Formik + Yup - Form state management & validation
- Axios - HTTP client with JWT interceptors
- React Context API - State management
- Recharts - Data visualization
- React Toastify - Notifications

